cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use convo-recall in research, please cite it as below."
title: "convo-recall: searchable conversation memory for AI coding agents"
abstract: >-
  A local-first SQLite + FTS5 + sqlite-vec hybrid search tool that indexes
  Claude Code, Codex, and Gemini session transcripts. Provides time-decay
  reranking, secret redaction at ingest, and a UNIX-socket embedding sidecar
  (BAAI/bge-large-en-v1.5).
authors:
